Package com.example.luckydragon.Views

Class EventView

java.lang.Object
com.example.luckydragon.Views.Observer
com.example.luckydragon.Views.EventView
public class EventView extends Observer
The EventView class is the View managed by the EventActivity. Handles displaying the event information and updating it if the Event model changes.
